<span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p><strong>② 多线程环境使用原子类保证线程安全（基本数据类型）</strong></p>
<div class="language-java ext-java line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-java"><code><span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">Test2</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
